7 NEW SECTION. Section 2. Exemption from lap-shoulder belt requirement. [Section 1] does not
8 apply to:
9 (1) a school bus purchased prior to January 1, 2026; or
10 (2) a school bus purchased on or after January 1, 2026, if the board of trustees for the school
11 district:
12 (a) determines that the school district's budget does not permit the school district to purchase a
13 school bus equipped with lap-shoulder belts as required by [section 1] based on actual market prices for the
14 school bus to be purchased; and
15 (b) votes to approve the determination in subsection (2)(a) in a public meeting that is officially
16 recorded and made available under 2-3-212.
